reviews.text: I have had dental work done in many countries in Europe and the America's. I have had some good experiences but nothing as smooth as Dr. Boey. Dr. He takes pictures during the procedure (I had a triple root canal) and applies the Novocain in stages, unlike a few clinics I have been to, giving it time to act so you feel nothing. I have had dozens of teeth worked on. This was the best numbing technique I have ever encountered. I was really worried I was going to feel some pain. There was none. Nothing. Incredible. It's such a pleasure to be guided down a path to a well executed procedure by someone that really knows what he is doing. He explained what he was doing and why, I felt totally safe.
